title: China Imbiss Bistro Wok
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Thai, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan options include mini vegetarian spring rolls, Thai curry with vegetable and coconut, mixed Chinese vegetables, fried rice with mixed Chinese vegetables, fried noodles with mixed Chinese vegetable (vegans to specify and request "no egg"). All dishes come with rice. NOTE: that all dishes contain MSG but can be prepared without it upon request. Menu is in German only.
